Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.30,0:00:09.72,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] And yet,\Nshe did grant my wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.80,0:00:12.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Holding up her end of this\Nperverse contract, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.80,0:00:15.27,Main,,0,0,0,,And I became an Eternal Girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.35,0:00:17.02,Main,,0,0,0,,To repeat the cycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.10,0:00:19.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Get it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.39,0:00:21.44,Main,,0,0,0,,That's the ugly truth\Nbehind this game!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.52,0:00:22.94,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.69,0:00:27.11,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.61,0:00:32.03,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.70,0:00:36.99,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.08,0:00:37.91,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Hitoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.00,0:00:39.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.47,0:00:52.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh my gosh! Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.01,0:00:54.39,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Ruko!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.47,0:00:56.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Go get help! Call an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.02,0:00:58.68,Main,,0,0,0,,But I don't have\Na cell phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.77,0:00:59.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Come on, think.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.77,0:01:02.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Hitoe has\None! Just hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.27,0:01:04.40,Main,,0,0,0,,What? Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.91,0:02:40.28,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Yeah, nothing serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.37,0:02:42.95,Main,,0,0,0,,The doctor said\Nshe's stable now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.04,0:02:44.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.75,0:02:46.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they called them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.54,0:02:49.71,Main,,0,0,0,,I hope this is okay, but,\NI, uh, I wanted to wait
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.79,0:02:51.34,Main,,0,0,0,,with Hitoe a bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.42,0:02:54.63,Main,,0,0,0,,You know, until her\Nparents show up at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.72,0:02:56.93,Main,,0,0,0,,[HATSU] Sure. That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.01,0:02:58.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Of course you can\Nstay with your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.01,0:03:01.89,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm just glad you called.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.97,0:03:06.98,Main,,0,0,0,,But--how are you? I'm worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.06,0:03:09.81,Main,,0,0,0,,No, don't. I'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.90,0:03:12.73,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll call again if\Nanything else comes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.49,0:03:14.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.50,0:03:34.96,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Why didn't\NI listen to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.05,0:03:36.47,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.22,0:03:41.35,Main,,0,0,0,,I should've stopped\Nwhile I had the chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.43,0:03:42.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Yuzuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.93,0:03:44.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you know how this happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.56,0:03:46.43,Main,,0,0,0,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.52,0:03:52.11,Main,,0,0,0,,I won the battle and then,\Nwell, it was strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.19,0:03:55.11,Main,,0,0,0,,[VOICE] And now...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.19,0:03:57.19,Main,,0,0,0,,You become an LRIG.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.41,0:04:05.04,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.29,0:04:14.17,Main,,0,0,0,,What's... going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.25,0:04:15.67,Main,,0,0,0,,[VOICE] Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.75,0:04:17.17,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.76,0:04:22.18,Main,,0,0,0,,[VOICE] Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.56,0:04:26.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.98,0:04:29.73,Main,,0,0,0,,My name is... Mayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.86,0:04:34.23,Main,,0,0,0,,That's insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.31,0:04:36.86,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] It was like some sort\Nof weird initiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.94,0:04:39.15,Main,,0,0,0,,She told me all about\NSelectors, LRIGs,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.24,0:04:40.99,Main,,0,0,0,,and how Eternal Girls work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.07,0:04:42.24,Main,,0,0,0,,If you become an LRIG,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.32,0:04:45.04,Main,,0,0,0,,then apparently\Nyou wake up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.12,0:04:47.41,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] You think Hanayo went\Nthrough the same thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.50,0:04:48.91,Main,,0,0,0,,I would imagine so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.00,0:04:50.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Mayu...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.29,0:04:51.42,Main,,0,0,0,,A white room...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.50,0:04:52.88,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Wh- Tama?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.96,0:04:54.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you know something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.71,0:04:57.00,Main,,0,0,0,,My memory is\Nstill too fuzzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.09,0:05:00.22,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] So, who is\Nthis "Mayu" girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.30,0:05:03.01,Main,,0,0,0,,I dunno, she didn't\Ntalk about herself much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.09,0:05:04.89,Main,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.97,0:05:06.35,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] I know\Nwhat you're thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.43,0:05:08.68,Main,,0,0,0,,That Hanayo was tricking me\Nthis entire time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.77,0:05:09.27,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.35,0:05:10.69,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.77,0:05:12.27,Main,,0,0,0,,She didn't mention a word\Nabout her taking my place,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.35,0:05:13.44,Main,,0,0,0,,or any of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.52,0:05:15.56,Main,,0,0,0,,If what Mayu\Ntold me is true,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.65,0:05:18.36,Main,,0,0,0,,she's out there living\Nmy life right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.44,0:05:21.20,Main,,0,0,0,,All that talk about\Nhelping me with my wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.28,0:05:23.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Figured she was laughing\Nat me the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.57,0:05:24.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.49,0:05:26.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, that's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.95,0:05:28.58,Main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.66,0:05:30.33,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Hanayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.41,0:05:32.04,Main,,0,0,0,,How could you do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.12,0:05:33.25,Main,,0,0,0,,We were friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.33,0:05:35.17,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU] Don't blame her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.25,0:05:38.25,Main,,0,0,0,,LRIGs are not allowed to share\Nthe truth with their Selectors.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.34,0:05:41.26,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Why do you know\Nthis and nobody else?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.34,0:05:42.55,Main,,0,0,0,,What is this place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.63,0:05:44.05,Main,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.72,0:05:48.93,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU] If this rule is broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.01,0:05:52.06,Main,,0,0,0,,If their Selector learns the\Ntruth and refuses to battle
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.14,0:05:55.23,Main,,0,0,0,,anymore, that LRIG will\Nforever lose her chance
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.31,0:05:57.82,Main,,0,0,0,,to escape the world\Ninside her card.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.69,0:06:02.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Then you're doing it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.24,0:06:06.12,Main,,0,0,0,,You're trying to\Ntrick poor Hitoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.20,0:06:08.08,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.16,0:06:09.70,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll try to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.25,0:06:16.83,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.92,0:06:20.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you, Selector.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.92,0:06:22.42,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] I couldn't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.51,0:06:26.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe became a Selector\Nagain and I was her LRIG.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.76,0:06:28.51,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.60,0:06:30.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Should I hide the\Ntruth from her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.60,0:06:34.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Was it my job to\Nforce her into battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.44,0:06:38.81,Main,,0,0,0,,At the very least, I knew I'd be\Nstuck in this card if I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.90,0:06:40.36,Main,,0,0,0,,But after what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.28,0:06:44.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's be friends, Hitoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.49,0:06:47.28,Main,,0,0,0,,How do-- How do\Nyou know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.37,0:06:48.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.66,0:06:51.24,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Well, let's just\Nsay I'm magic, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.25,0:06:57.21,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Even though we\Ndidn't know her for long,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.29,0:06:59.46,Main,,0,0,0,,I still felt like we\Nwere good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.54,0:07:01.21,Main,,0,0,0,,But after her wish\Nwas corrupted,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.30,0:07:03.55,Main,,0,0,0,,she really did forget about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.63,0:07:06.76,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm your LRIG now,\Nso take good care of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.84,0:07:09.30,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] LRIG? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.39,0:07:11.60,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] For starters,\Ncan you tell me your wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.68,0:07:15.27,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] My wish...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.35,0:07:18.10,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Yeah, if you have one,\NI can make it come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.19,0:07:20.11,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm Yuzuki, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.19,0:07:22.19,Main,,0,0,0,,I think you and I\Nwill be good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.27,0:07:25.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Yu... zu... ki...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.24,0:07:29.20,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.28,0:07:30.49,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.57,0:07:32.41,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] "I've gotta fight\Nmy way outta here."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.49,0:07:35.12,Main,,0,0,0,,"Even if I have to\Nhurt Hitoe to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.20,0:07:38.00,Main,,0,0,0,,I need to see Kazuki again."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.08,0:07:39.58,Main,,0,0,0,,That was all I could think.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.29,0:07:43.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't be shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.42,0:07:46.38,Main,,0,0,0,,You must have a wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.47,0:07:47.88,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] I-I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.14,0:07:51.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE'S MOTHER] Hitoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.22,0:07:54.06,Main,,0,0,0,,You okay? Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.14,0:07:56.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Talk to me, Hitoe! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.06,0:07:59.31,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] I knew her wish\Nwas already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.40,0:08:02.11,Main,,0,0,0,,But what could I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.19,0:08:04.86,Main,,0,0,0,,This was the only\Nchance given to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.94,0:08:07.95,Main,,0,0,0,,I had to take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.03,0:08:09.45,Main,,0,0,0,,But then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.28,0:08:16.33,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Just as I was starting\Nto think I'd have to give up,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.41,0:08:20.00,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess I got lucky and\Nsomething happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.93,0:08:37.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.31,0:08:39.31,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.39,0:08:39.98,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE grunts in pain]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.06,0:08:41.06,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Oh my gosh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.15,0:08:42.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.86,0:08:44.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.27,0:08:46.48,Main,,0,0,0,,If it hurts, why are you\Nputting yourself through this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.57,0:08:48.11,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.19,0:08:51.16,Main,,0,0,0,,I just... feel like...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.24,0:08:53.20,Main,,0,0,0,,This is something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.66,0:08:59.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] But I think,\Nmaybe, I do have a wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.79,0:09:01.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.21,0:09:05.50,Main,,0,0,0,,I wanna have friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.59,0:09:08.92,Main,,0,0,0,,And for some reason that hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.34,0:09:14.60,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] After all the horrible\Nthings she went through.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.68,0:09:16.81,Main,,0,0,0,,All that pain and confusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.10,0:09:21.98,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] She still asked\Nfor the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.98,0:09:27.61,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.69,0:09:29.28,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] Can I have friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.36,0:09:31.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Can you do that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.13,0:09:46.21,Main,,0,0,0,,You have my word.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.29,0:09:48.34,Main,,0,0,0,,I promise I'll make\Nyour wish come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.92,0:09:52.97,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] How could I say no\Nto a crying girl, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.05,0:09:54.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Whether it was right or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.51,0:09:56.76,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess I got caught\Nup in the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.73,0:10:08.48,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Will Hitoe's wish\Nturn out like mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.57,0:10:13.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Even I can make it come true,\Nis it really worth the cost?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.20,0:10:17.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Makes me wonder if Hanayo\Nwent through all this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.78,0:10:21.41,Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder if she felt as\Nlost and hurt as I do now
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.50,0:10:23.79,Main,,0,0,0,,And if her wish came true...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.87,0:10:25.38,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI cries softly]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.46,0:10:26.84,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Hanayo...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.92,0:10:28.34,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI sobs]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.63,0:10:35.97,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] After that,\NI started to rethink things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.05,0:10:38.22,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Hey, Hitoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.30,0:10:41.10,Main,,0,0,0,,If you want your\Nwish to come true,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.18,0:10:44.02,Main,,0,0,0,,we'll have to find a battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.10,0:10:46.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll try...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.19,0:10:48.90,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] I intentionally\Nhad her battle you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.98,0:10:52.03,Main,,0,0,0,,And then told you the\Ntruth in front of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.11,0:10:54.03,Main,,0,0,0,,So it's not quite\Nwhat it looked like.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.11,0:10:57.41,Main,,0,0,0,,I was hoping she'd refuse to\Nfight after she heard that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.49,0:10:58.87,Main,,0,0,0,,But, if she quit,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.95,0:11:01.20,Main,,0,0,0,,then you'd be stuck in the\Ncard forever, wouldn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.29,0:11:02.20,Main,,0,0,0,,That doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.29,0:11:03.41,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.50,0:11:05.21,Main,,0,0,0,,She's my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.29,0:11:11.00,Main,,0,0,0,,If I have to sacrifice her, then\NI might as well just disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.09,0:11:15.92,Main,,0,0,0,,And besides, if I can't live\Nas Yuzuki Kurebayashi anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.01,0:11:19.89,Main,,0,0,0,,If I can't even love\NKazuki as myself anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.97,0:11:21.68,Main,,0,0,0,,then what's the point?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.76,0:11:22.93,Main,,0,0,0,,I give up...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.02,0:11:24.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.48,0:11:26.27,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE'S MOTHER] Hitoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.35,0:11:28.77,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Uh, hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.86,0:11:30.65,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE'S MOTHER] Oh, Ruko!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.73,0:11:32.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Where's Hitoe? Is she okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.69,0:11:34.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh, yeah, everything\Nis just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.94,0:11:36.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Mostly, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.40,0:11:38.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Seems like she's\Ncalmed down now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.45,0:11:40.74,Main,,0,0,0,,The doctor's with her.\NYou can go inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.83,0:11:42.83,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE'S MOTHER gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.91,0:11:46.00,Main,,0,0,0,,[groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.08,0:11:49.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.80,0:11:55.09,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm just scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.17,0:11:56.76,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.84,0:12:00.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe was... She was\Nso sweet before...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.64,0:12:03.85,Main,,0,0,0,,But now, I don't know\Nwhat's going on in her head.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.93,0:12:05.89,Main,,0,0,0,,It's terrifying...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.98,0:12:07.39,Main,,0,0,0,,What am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.48,0:12:10.36,Main,,0,0,0,,What can I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.44,0:12:14.02,Main,,0,0,0,,It's like I don't even\Nknow her anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.11,0:12:15.65,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm at a loss...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.75,0:12:32.25,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.34,0:12:33.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.42,0:12:36.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Can I take you to\Nmy place for now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.30,0:12:37.47,Main,,0,0,0,,This is all my fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.55,0:12:38.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.80,0:12:40.76,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] I was the one\Nwho made her battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.85,0:12:44.01,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.10,0:12:46.77,Main,,0,0,0,,But... you just wanted\Nto help, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.43,0:12:51.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Even though the truth was\Nmore than Hitoe could take,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.56,0:12:54.57,Main,,0,0,0,,your intentions\Nwere still noble.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.65,0:12:57.86,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Thank you, Ruko...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.94,0:12:59.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah! I just realized.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.90,0:13:02.37,Main,,0,0,0,,This'll be the second\Ntime you've stayed over!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.45,0:13:03.78,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Oh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.87,0:13:05.33,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.41,0:13:09.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Actually, before we go back,\Ncan we stop somewhere for a sec?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.14,0:13:26.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Is this good?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.39,0:13:28.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Can you see from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.60,0:13:31.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.44,0:13:33.81,Main,,0,0,0,,[LANDLADY] Well, if it\Nisn't Yuzuki and Kazuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.90,0:13:34.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Are ya steppin' out?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.98,0:13:36.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Just to the\Nconvenience store.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.61,0:13:39.11,Main,,0,0,0,,[LANDLADY] Looks like we've\Ngot snow coming, so be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.19,0:13:40.28,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO (Y)] Yes ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.36,0:13:42.07,Main,,0,0,0,,[KAZUKI] See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.83,0:13:51.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki, something\Nbothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.13,0:14:00.55,Main,,0,0,0,,[KAZUKI grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.93,0:14:05.97,Main,,0,0,0,,What's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.05,0:14:07.89,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to be\Nboyfriend and girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.97,0:14:09.85,Main,,0,0,0,,[KAZUKI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.93,0:14:11.60,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.68,0:14:13.23,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.35,0:14:15.52,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO (Y)]\NThis is the only time
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.61,0:14:17.69,Main,,0,0,0,,we can be together as lovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.77,0:14:20.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Mom and Dad are still\Nupstairs watching TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.44,0:14:22.82,Main,,0,0,0,,No one from school's\Nhere to see us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.90,0:14:25.99,Main,,0,0,0,,In weather like this, if we\Nhappen to share an umbrella,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.07,0:14:28.78,Main,,0,0,0,,no one will bat an eye, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.71,0:14:35.13,Main,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.99,0:15:03.40,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.57,0:15:06.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Aw, isn't it beautiful, Kazuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.61,0:15:09.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Snowing, just for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.33,0:15:15.83,Main,,0,0,0,,You really are\Nstrong, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.91,0:15:17.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.33,0:15:19.88,Main,,0,0,0,,[KAZUKI] You've been like that\Never since were little.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.96,0:15:21.71,Main,,0,0,0,,You always protected me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.80,0:15:26.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Kept me on the right path.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.34,0:15:28.51,Main,,0,0,0,,I should've told you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.60,0:15:31.85,Main,,0,0,0,,For my entire life,\NI've loved you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.77,0:15:39.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.19,0:15:41.23,Main,,0,0,0,,But I want to protect you, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.32,0:15:42.78,Main,,0,0,0,,As your brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.86,0:15:44.69,Main,,0,0,0,,...and your boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.04,0:15:58.46,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.88,0:16:03.30,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.97,0:16:16.48,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] She made my wish\Ncome true, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.56,0:16:19.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Even though she took my body,\Nshe still kept her word.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.69,0:16:22.48,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI cries softly]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.57,0:16:25.57,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Thank you, Hanayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.65,0:16:27.28,Main,,0,0,0,,You were my friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.92,0:16:46.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzu... ki...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.63,0:16:52.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH] Setting your little\Nplan into motion, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.22,0:16:53.60,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.68,0:16:54.68,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH] I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.76,0:16:56.18,Main,,0,0,0,,You think she'll really come?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.27,0:16:57.52,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA] Oh, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.60,0:16:59.52,Main,,0,0,0,,She'll come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.60,0:17:01.56,Main,,0,0,0,,She's the same as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.65,0:17:03.40,Main,,0,0,0,,I suppose that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.48,0:17:05.94,Main,,0,0,0,,And by that, I mean you both\Nhave WIXOSS on the brain
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.03,0:17:07.32,Main,,0,0,0,,and not much else.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.40,0:17:09.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Nothing personal, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.15,0:17:10.65,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.74,0:17:13.99,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH] Though I wonder if two\Nof you might be one too many.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.04,0:17:17.62,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] That doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.70,0:17:18.95,Main,,0,0,0,,She's my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.04,0:17:20.96,Main,,0,0,0,,If I have to sacrifice her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.04,0:17:23.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Then I might as\Nwell just disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.34,0:17:26.25,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] We're all still friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.34,0:17:29.72,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] She made my wish\Ncome true, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.80,0:17:33.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Even though she took my body,\Nshe still kept her word.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.64,0:17:37.02,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] If my wish\Ncame true, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.47,0:17:39.98,Main,,0,0,0,,"My wish?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.06,0:17:41.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Ugh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.45,0:17:54.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ru.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.95,0:17:56.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.12,0:17:58.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh, no, I'm fine,\Njust spacing out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.79,0:18:01.00,Main,,0,0,0,,So, what are you up to\Nout here, Grandma?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.08,0:18:02.50,Main,,0,0,0,,[HATSU] Nothing exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.58,0:18:03.88,Main,,0,0,0,,It started to snow,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.96,0:18:07.42,Main,,0,0,0,,so I'm trying to dry off the\Npotatoes I left outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.50,0:18:09.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Here, let me help.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.93,0:18:15.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Grandma?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.60,0:18:16.85,Main,,0,0,0,,[HATSU] Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.93,0:18:18.68,Main,,0,0,0,,All my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.77,0:18:22.35,Main,,0,0,0,,I never really wanted to\Nbe anything or do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.43,0:18:26.48,Main,,0,0,0,,And I didn't really care\Nif I had friends or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.56,0:18:28.40,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess that's\Nnot really normal,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.48,0:18:31.36,Main,,0,0,0,,so I can't blame\Nyou for worrying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.44,0:18:33.40,Main,,0,0,0,,But I've changed my mind now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.99,0:18:37.45,Main,,0,0,0,,[HATSU] Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.53,0:18:38.62,Main,,0,0,0,,I made friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.70,0:18:40.37,Main,,0,0,0,,And realized I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.45,0:18:41.50,Main,,0,0,0,,We had fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.58,0:18:43.16,Main,,0,0,0,,I was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.25,0:18:47.71,Main,,0,0,0,,I wanted to, I mean, I want to\Nstay with them forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.79,0:18:51.30,Main,,0,0,0,,So I mean, I guess\Nwhat I'm asking is
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.38,0:18:53.59,Main,,0,0,0,,if there's anything\NI can do for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.18,0:18:59.31,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'll come up\Nwith something on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.39,0:19:00.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.43,0:19:01.85,Main,,0,0,0,,I have faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.93,0:19:04.89,Main,,0,0,0,,You are my Ru after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.98,0:19:06.60,Main,,0,0,0,,You can do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.78,0:19:13.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Heh. Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.11,0:19:14.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.28,0:19:16.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Guess we can't put\Nthem back outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.87,0:19:19.83,Main,,0,0,0,,No, but maybe over there, where\Nthey can still get some sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.91,0:19:21.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.04,0:19:29.09,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Tama?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.17,0:19:31.30,Main,,0,0,0,,You're acting weird...\NWhat's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.68,0:19:41.35,Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder if you were like\Nme when you were a real girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.60,0:19:45.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Bet you had all sorts\Nof friends, back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.06,0:19:48.19,Main,,0,0,0,,It'd be fun to find out\Nwhat kind of wish y--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.27,0:19:49.69,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.77,0:19:51.73,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.82,0:19:54.11,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't remember\Nany of that stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.40,0:19:56.53,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.61,0:19:59.03,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] I didn't know\Nthat other stuff either!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.12,0:20:01.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Not about Selectors\Nswitching with LRIGS
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.20,0:20:03.12,Main,,0,0,0,,or wishes or the weird room!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.20,0:20:04.37,Main,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't lie to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.45,0:20:05.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Please believe me, Ru!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.83,0:20:08.46,Main,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to battle\Ntogether, I promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.75,0:20:12.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Of course I believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.59,0:20:13.25,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] You mean it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.34,0:20:14.21,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.30,0:20:15.51,Main,,0,0,0,,You're my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.59,0:20:17.17,Main,,0,0,0,,We have to trust each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.72,0:20:21.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Guess you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.81,0:20:23.85,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.93,0:20:27.18,Main,,0,0,0,,It sure has been\Na long day, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.27,0:20:28.73,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm going to bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.48,0:20:32.90,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Night-night, Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.12,0:20:44.49,Main,,0,0,0,,[computer keys\Nclacking sporadiccaly]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.58,0:20:45.87,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO grunts softly]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.95,0:20:47.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Wha...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.12,0:20:49.29,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.37,0:20:50.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL 10A] Hey,\Ndid you see this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.79,0:20:53.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL 10B] Yeah, the Iona\Nfan event thing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.80,0:20:54.88,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Ah...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.96,0:20:55.96,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL 10B] But on the ad,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.05,0:20:57.88,Main,,0,0,0,,it said it's only for\N"select" people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.97,0:20:59.93,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL 10A] Do you have to win\Na contest or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.01,0:21:01.59,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL 10B] It didn't seem\Nlike it, but I dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.68,0:21:03.68,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL 10C] There's no\Naddress listed either.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.76,0:21:05.93,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL 10A] It doesn't list\Nanything but a contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.02,0:21:07.43,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL 10D] Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.52,0:21:10.48,Main,,0,0,0,,I sent them an e-mail about it,\Nbut I didn't get a reply.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.56,0:21:12.73,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL 10C] What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.81,0:21:14.23,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Ruko!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.44,0:21:16.57,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] We gotta\Nfind that thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.65,0:21:18.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Do a search for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.74,0:21:20.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Try typing: "Iona Fan Event."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.74,0:21:22.62,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Uh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.37,0:21:31.79,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] What is it, Ru?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.29,0:21:37.51,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] An Iona fan event,\Njust like they said.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.59,0:21:40.22,Main,,0,0,0,,"To those who are\Nforced to select."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.30,0:21:43.01,Main,,0,0,0,,"To those who do not\Nrefuse to select."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.09,0:21:46.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Then it has hashtag\N"Selector" at the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.51,0:21:48.85,Main,,0,0,0,,So, what do you guys\Nthink she's trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.18,0:21:51.10,Main,,0,0,0,,She's calling us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.19,0:21:52.35,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.44,0:21:54.31,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] She's bringing\Nthe Selectors together.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.83,0:23:35.54,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] It's happening\Nreally close to here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.62,0:23:36.88,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.96,0:23:37.92,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] I don't want to hear it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.00,0:23:39.42,Main,,0,0,0,,and I have nothing\Nto say to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.50,0:23:41.46,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] I'm sure my\Nplan is gonna work.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.55,0:23:43.05,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] No! I don't want to!
